            </span>
            <span class="vt-duration">2:51</span>
          </div>
          <div class="vt-meta">
            <h3 class="vt-name">Daniel Cohen</h3>
            <span class="vt-business">Atlas Logistics</span>
            <span class="vt-tag" data-tag="webapp">Web App</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="vt-card" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-label="Play video testimonial from Andrea Reyes, Lake Scaping LLC">
          <div class="vt-thumb bg-2">
            <span class="vt-play" aria-hidden="true">
              <span><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><polygon points="6 4 20 12 6 20 6 4"></polygon></svg></span>
            </span>
            <span class="vt-duration">2:08</span>
          </div>
          <div class="vt-meta">
            <h3 class="vt-name">Andrea Reyes</h3>
            <span class="vt-business">Lake Scaping LLC</span>
            <span class="vt-tag" data-tag="web-design">Web Design</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="vt-card" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-label="Play video testimonial from Thiago Moreira, Solé Roofing Group">
          <div class="vt-thumb bg-8">
            <span class="vt-play" aria-hidden="true">
              <span><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><polygon points="6 4 20 12 6 20 6 4"></polygon></svg></span>
            </span>
            <span class="vt-duration">1:42</span>
          </div>
          <div class="vt-meta">
            <h3 class="vt-name">Thiago Moreira</h3>
            <span class="vt-business">Solé Roofing Group</span>
            <span class="vt-tag" data-tag="marketing">Marketing</span>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       GOOGLE REVIEWS
       ============================================================ -->
  <div class="green-bg">
    <img class="figure f1" src="/images/figure-bg-3.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true">
    <img class="figure f2" src="/images/figure-bg-2.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true">
