          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow">Google Reviews</div>
            <h2>Trusted by Businesses Across South Florida</h2>
            <p>Verified reviews on Google from contractors, e-commerce brands, and service operators we've helped grow since 2021.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="gr-rating">
            <div class="gr-score">
              5.0
              <span class="gr-score-stars" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg></span>
            </div>
            <span class="gr-meta">From <strong>47 verified reviews</strong> on Google</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="gr-grid" data-elfsight-app-id="d2ce1169-e2c8-43d7-873d-f9e6f7bc1e07" data-reveal-children>
          
        <article class="gr-card">
          <span class="gr-quote" aria-hidden="true">"</span>
          <div class="gr-stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg></div>
          <p class="gr-text">Senavia rebuilt our roofing company website and within two months we doubled our qualified leads. The team is detail-oriented, communicative, and clearly knows local SEO inside out.</p>
          <div class="gr-author">
            <span class="gr-avatar a1" aria-hidden="true">CR</span>
            <div class="gr-author-info">
              <span class="gr-author-name">Carlos Rivera</span>
              <span class="gr-author-date">2 weeks ago</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="gr-card">
          <span class="gr-quote" aria-hidden="true">"</span>
          <div class="gr-stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg></div>
          <p class="gr-text">Their design work elevated our brand instantly — modern, fast, and converting. We&apos;ve climbed three Google ranking positions for our main keywords since launch. Highly recommend.</p>
          <div class="gr-author">
            <span class="gr-avatar a2" aria-hidden="true">MG</span>
            <div class="gr-author-info">
              <span class="gr-author-name">Maria Gonzalez</span>
              <span class="gr-author-date">1 month ago</span>
            </div>
